Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan backtracks on missiles
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wnjv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Nov 1981
Protests prompt President Reagan to suggest US and Soviet re-think on deploying land-based missiles. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less